BTTAdditionalActions.BTTPredefinedActionName: Close currently open Touch Bar group
Close currently open Touch Bar group

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: tell application "Google Chrome"	set selectedText to (execute active tab of front window javascript "(''+getSelection())")	if selectedText = "" then		return "No text"	else if length of selectedText > 100 then		return "Text too long"	else		try			set a to selectedText as number			return ""		end try		return do shell script "/usr/local/Cellar/translate-shell/0.9.6.5/bin/trans :pl -brief '" & selectedText & "'"	end ifend tell
